---
title: add_polynomialcoeff (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_order : order a, b so len(a) >= len(b)
    q_order --> q_lengths : length_a = len(a), length_b = len(b)
    q_lengths --> q_iter : i < length_a
    q_iter --> q_add : result[i] = a[i] + (b[i] if i < length_b else 0)
    q_add --> q_iter : i < length_a
    q_add --> q_return : i >= length_a
    q_return --> [*] : return PolynomialCoeff(result)

    note right of q_iter
        INV: Result degree = max(deg(a), deg(b))
        INV: Shorter polynomial is zero-padded for missing coefficients
    end note
